:book: *Porygon-Z Commands*

> `!workspace` ‚Äî Configure workspace settings (directory, model, effort, permissions, channel response mode)
> `!cd <path>` ‚Äî Change the working directory for this channel
> `!ll` ‚Äî List files in the current working directory
> `!kill` ‚Äî Kill running Claude processes in this channel
> `!kill-all` ‚Äî Kill all running Claude processes globally
> `!sessions` ‚Äî List active Claude sessions
> `!help` ‚Äî Show this help message

*Usage:*
> `!workspace` ‚Äî Show current configuration
> `!workspace model=sonnet effort=high` ‚Äî Update settings
> `!workspace prompt="custom instruction"` ‚Äî Set workspace instruction
> Keys: `cwd`, `model`, `effort`, `permission`, `response`, `prompt`